<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4907795>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 19. Sagola species in the pulchra species-group. Habitus, dorsal views: a) S. pulchra, b) S. keejeongi, c) S. ramsayi, d) S. poortmani. Aedeagi, dorsal views: e) S. pulchra, f) S. keejeongi, g) S. ramsayi, h) S. poortmani. S. keejeongi, male: i) Dorsal surface of head, j) Ventral surface of head (arrow indicates lateral process), k) Mid-leg, lateral view. S. pulchra, female: l) Ventrite VIII, ventral view, m) Ventrite IX, ventral view. Scale bars a–d = 1 mm, e–m = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4907795/files/figure.png" .

